README.md
     1вҶ’# Versioning Library for Go
     6вҶ’go-version is a library for parsing versions and version constraints,
     7вҶ’and verifying versions against a set of constraints. go-version
     8вҶ’can sort a collection of versions properly, handles prerelease/beta
     9вҶ’versions, can increment versions, etc.
    10вҶ’
    11вҶ’Versions used with go-version must follow [SemVer](http://semver.org/).
    12вҶ’
    13вҶ’## Installation and Usage
    15вҶ’Package documentation can be found on
    16вҶ’[Go Reference](https://pkg.go.dev/github.com/hashicorp/go-version).
    17вҶ’
    18вҶ’Installation can be done with a normal `go get`:
    19вҶ’
    20вҶ’```
    21вҶ’$ go get github.com/hashicorp/go-version
    22вҶ’```
    23вҶ’
